	   <tr><td colspan=2>You can get to 250 jeweling for a couple of thousand plat.<br>The really expensive skill to master is that frigging tailoring.<br>Wu's armor maxes at 148ish i think.<br>The next highest trivial Item to tailor is veliuos armors which are never trivial even at 250 skill, some of these pelts you need cost upwards of 500+pp each.<br><br>&nbsp;<br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=39279 target=_new><span style='color: green;'>Crackercrumbs</span style='color: green;'></a><br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=35339 target=_new><span style='color: maroon;'>Willyj</span style='color: maroon;'></a></td></tr>
